<br />
&ldquo;Takumi is an incredible player and we didn&rsquo;t give him enough chances, that&rsquo;s the truth. Southampton makes a lot sense. He&rsquo;s there for 17 games. If he stays fit there&rsquo;s a good chance he will play 17 games. That helps them, it helps us. Takumi was always a long-term project and he still is. I hope it&rsquo;s a win-win situation.&rdquo;

